author: CBS News
title: Maryland calls in National Guard to prepare for virus surge
description: The National Guard's mission is to prepare for the surge of fatalities the state expects to come in mid-April,
content: Maryland's National Guard has stepped up to help the state prepare for their own coronavirus surge, which Governor Larry Hogan says is "about two weeks behind New York." The National Guard has set up cots for a field hospital at a Baltimore convention center,… [+2119 chars]
